1. *Pićem* razbijemo led na stazi. (Using a drink, we break the ice on the path.)
2. Često se družimo uz *piće* posle posla. (*Drink* is often the thing we gather around after work.)
3. Pit ću vodu jer sam žedna, a ti možeš odabrati neko drugo *piće*. (I will drink water because I'm thirsty, and you can choose another *drink*.)
4. Oni su uživali u egzotičnim *pićima* tokom letovanja. (They enjoyed exotic *drinks* during their summer vacation.)
5. Ovaj *napitak* sadrži med i limun. (This *beverage* contains honey and lemon.)
6. U kafiću možete poručiti različita *pića*, uključujući kafu i čaj. (In a café, you can order various *drinks*, including coffee and tea.)
7. Da li si isprobao novo *piće* koje su uveli u meni? (Have you tried the new *drink* they added to the menu?)
8. *Piće* je toliko toplo da ne mogu ni da ga dotaknem. (*The drink* is so hot that I can't even touch it.)